\fs32 Summary:\par
\fs24 my_DEX is an innovative concept for a fully decentralized cryptocurrency trading platform built upon the Bitcoin Lightning Network as a Layer-2 protocol. The project aims to combine lightning-fast off-chain transactions with maximum security, true decentralization, and a robust node compensation system. In contrast to existing solutions (e.g., Bisq), my_DEX strives for a genuinely decentralized architecture without central entities or hidden control points. The open-source project will be published under the GPLv3.0 license, the core is implemented in Rust, and it offers a user-friendly interface catering to a wide audience\f1\emdash\f0 from technically proficient traders to beginners without extensive knowledge. Below we outline the vision and motivation, the underlying technology and architecture, governance and security principles, the compensation model, aspects of usability, and the requirement for an interdisciplinary development team.\par
\par
\fs32 1. Vision and Motivation\par
\b\fs24 Long-term Vision: \b0 my_DEX aims to create a truly decentralized exchange that embodies the ideals of the crypto community. At its core is the vision of a marketplace operating completely trustlessly\f1\emdash\f0 each user retains full control over their coins, while trades occur atomically and without intermediaries. Leveraging the Lightning Network as its technological backbone, my_DEX achieves transaction speeds and costs that significantly outperform conventional on-chain DEXs or centralized exchanges. Simultaneously, the system remains resilient against censorship and failures, as it has no single point of failure.\par
\par
\b Motivation and Problem Statement\b0 : The impetus for my_DEX arose from the limitations of existing "decentralized" exchanges. Projects like Bisq, while often labeled decentralized, exhibit practical shortcomings such as slow on-chain settlement, limited trading pairs, and occasionally centralized elements (e.g., dispute mediators or central seed servers for network connections). From our founder's perspective, such solutions are only superficially decentralized. Moreover, many current DEX offerings are either tied to a single blockchain (often Ethereum) or technically demanding to operate. The consequences include slow trades, high fees, and barriers to mainstream adoption.\par
\par
my_DEX addresses these shortcomings with a novel approach:\par

\pard{\pntext\f4\'B7\tab}{\*\pn\pnlvlblt\pnf4\pnindent0{\pntxtb\'B7}}\fi-360\li720\sa200\sl276\slmult1\b True Decentralization\b0 : All trading components\f1\emdash\f0 from order matching to settlement\f1\emdash\f0 run distributed across a peer-to-peer network of nodes, without central servers or authorities.\par
{\pntext\f4\'B7\tab}\b Lightning-Fast Transactions\b0 : By building upon the Lightning Network (Layer 2), transactions are executed virtually in real-time with minimal fees, irrespective of the main blockchain's load.\par
{\pntext\f4\'B7\tab}\b Trustless Settlement\b0 : Through Hashed Timelock Contracts (HTLCs) and atomic swaps (see Section 2), different coins can be exchanged directly between participants without the need to trust a third party.\par
{\pntext\f4\'B7\tab}\b Accessible to Everyone\b0 : The platform is designed to be so user-friendly that even non-technical users can participate as traders or even as node operators (see Section 5). Only broad participation ensures that decentralization is not merely theoretical but a practical reality.\par

\pard\sa200\sl276\slmult1\b Role of the Founder and Development Approach:\b0  Interestingly, the initial prototype of my_DEX was not created by a classical programmer but by the founder himself, who designed a basic framework with the support of AI (GPT-4). This unconventional approach\f1\emdash\f0 a non-developer leveraging AI to build foundational software\f1\emdash\f0 highlights the motivation to quickly achieve innovative results and push boundaries. Naturally, an interdisciplinary developer team will now build upon this foundation to transform the vision into a secure, efficient, and user-friendly product. The collaboration of various experts (Rust development, UI/UX, cryptography, etc., see Section 6) ensures the initial concept is professionally implemented and sustainably maintained. In summary, my_DEX is driven by the vision of creating an inclusive, ultra-fast, and truly decentralized marketplace that merges trust in cryptographic systems with practical everyday usability. This motivation underpins all subsequent technical and organizational decisions.\par
